Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dama in friendlies is punishable by MCD
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi Hideyoshi, King of the Negatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Born and raised in Chiba prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oda Shintarou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A "play by feel" master of Ippatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Born in Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokugawa Yasube
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,An absolute nyagger with zero knowledge on theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Born in Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Akechi Kouichi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A by-the-book calculative and\N reasoning-dependent player.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Born in Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayami Akina
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically Toyotomi's girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Born with incredible luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Born in Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,/mjg/ presents Super Zugan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, there it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:00:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy Birthday Zugan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Man since when were you the type\Nof guy to discard tiles like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna make it if you're the\Nsort to discard genbutsu to a riichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To make your read yet discard a harsh tile...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,By doing so your intuition will blossom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll be able to see through\Nthe opponent's tiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Looky looky!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.51,0:01:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, what'll you do with this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let it pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world kind of hand are you even making?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As it goes on, the one who riichi'd\Nwill be the one cowering instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're... really gonna discard that on haitei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That was... haitei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanyao nomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron on takame! Riichi Itsuu\NHaitei Dora 1 Ura 1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugaaaan~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Toyotomi here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Toyotomi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hayami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is, it's my birthday today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, is that so!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So would you like to come over for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's celebrate with the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in charge of menial things\Nsuch as cooking and the like so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi-kun can be in charge\Nof buying the cake, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,One of these decoration cakes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it someone's birthday today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe, yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you write it down as "Akina" for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I add "from an enviable\Nlittle guy" to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patronage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it your girlfriend's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on! Don't ask me the same thi-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For us to meet in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And what I see over there is a cake is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is-!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, might as well let us\Ndeliver the cake at this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} will be coming along as well, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Chop chop! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaaan~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Jansou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure bought a grand one didn't you?\NMust've cost a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet what happened to your fortune's\Nworth of dept, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,tweet twee-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tweet me, junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have you pay us back for\Neven a margin of that debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell's with a cake like this anyways!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Just let that cake be!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! If you can win, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat us and the cake shall be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chun, Menzen Honitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanyao, Pinfu, Dora 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi, Tsumo, Sanankou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, this is some tanoshii mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, why'd you always have\Nto make a grim face like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're spoiling the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Pinfu, Dora 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,2900 as dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I will win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll win and spend a very happy\Nbirthday with Akina!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on with that call and that pond?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been two hatsus discarded\Nalready as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's either an Itsuu made out of souzu\Nor a 123 shape sanshoku, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure doesn't learn, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanshoku Doukou Nomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a 2900 yoroshiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi did a renchan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time seeing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Tanyao Nomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo! Chun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As the three saw Toyotomi's renchan\Nfor the first time in their lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They could not help but make\Ntheir confusion apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet Toyotomi continued to stack his wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And at last...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,S4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's All Last with me leading 15000\Nabove the second place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm winning by a landslide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a dora ankou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! I got to tenpai as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm to aim for the hidden Sanshoku,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's best I cut South\Nfor the penchan on 7s.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But 7s is unlikely to come out of Toyotomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shintaro's riichi looks dangerous after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,On that note, Toyotomi's more\Nlikely to drop 8s as a one-chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll deliberately...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanki on the 9s!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Three riichis on the same turn huh? Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It came!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A 369 wait mangan! Chun Dora 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If it plays out well, sanankou stacks\Nas well raising it to haneman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by the discards, a 9s\Nhas 90% chances of passing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And as long as it doesn't connect to the dealer,\Nthere's no chances of a gyakuten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I won...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,With this... Victory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina-chan, I'll soon come to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Akina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Toyotomi- kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, this stew's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The salad's amazing too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Akina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought it almost looks\Nlike your birthday instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm really glad you came...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Riichi Ippatsu South Dora 1, 12000!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dahaha! Riichi Ippatsu\NPinfu Itsuu! That's 8000!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, we both read well didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You took the words right\Nout of my mouth friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, triple ron was allowed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye! Anything goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well sorry then, that's a ron from me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:09:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi Ippatsu Honroutou\NChiitoitsu Ura 2, 16000.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Su-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Super...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugaaaaan~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,SUPER\NZUGAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA\NAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you... I'll play another round so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch that cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, Toyotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wearing a rather nice\Njacket there ain't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Toyotomi, you dropped\Noff some spare change there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure got some nice things today, huh?\NSure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi-kun sure is late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If only...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If only he had left after slowly\Neating that cup ramen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He might have never even come across that trio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But alas...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He could not possibly know the true worth...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of this 129 yen cup of ramen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The true essence of mahjong\Nlies not in reading the pond...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Much more importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It is to pinpoint with precision what your\Nopponent is thinking in minute detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Like "Ah, this guy will sip on some\Ntea in exactly 30 seconds".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That musn't be 29 seconds or 31 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But to drink it in precisely 30 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what one must read!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasu will light a cig in the next 7 seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,1,2,3,4,5,6,7..!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,DID I DEAL IN?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Deal in, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi Sanankou Dora 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.14,0:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, give me the sticks already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"You can keep the change" you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, how generous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A tub...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, a tub!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected, Dejected
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's yet another riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, Genbutsu. He tightened up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The true essence of mahjong is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A breath holding race of four under a tub!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The first to come out of the water is the loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenpai! Kanchan wait on 5m!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, swim to the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come on already and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Menzen Honitsu Iipeikou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that? Look, tsumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hontoutou Chiitoitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo! Suuankou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina-chaaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Toyotomi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all due to that nightmare I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, nevermind! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to someday do the do with Akina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish for Toyotomi-kun to someday\Nstop playing mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's try drawing some\Nfortune telling slips!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I got 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I got 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet, Great Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you, Toyotomi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,JAPANESE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wanna try drawing another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,JAPANESE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,JAPANESE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one... Another one... Another one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,AnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnother\NAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOne\NAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnother\NAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOneAnotherOne\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you stop here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Givu me rasuto chansu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,JAPANESE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be 5000 yen for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But hey, even if it cost 5k, you managed to\Ndraw a Lesser Luck, so it all {\i1}paid{\i0} off didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like that resilient part\Nof yours, Toyotomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They're doing a dancing ritual over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong Toyotomi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you scared like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Jansou
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that dream was precognitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, it's such a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You might as well call it fate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't the three of you supposed to\Ngo to some hot springs this week?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And go we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just got this urge to\Nsee your face, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So we came back halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And unless we get some new years allowance\Nfrom you, we can't buy souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Ain't the slip a bit too small as it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasu... You just stay quiet, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But yeah, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, with hot spring manju being our starting\Ncash prize, let's start the first hanchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kokushi tenpai waiting tanki on South...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's already one in the ponds...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck it, riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shintaro's gimmick is ippatsu\Ntsumo after all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah, here comes a spicy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah, I should've riichi'd that one too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've won it with that 7s, but since\NI'm yakunashi I can't win off of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I have dora to boot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tsumo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! Yakuman, Kokushi Musou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! 5200!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sukaan~\N(zugan -> sukan = dead broke)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second! That south\NToyotomi just tsumogiri'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't called I'd have\Ntsumo'd then and there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think about it in\Nthe heat of the moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sukan-po~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What an unlucky man I am!\NAt this pace... I'll never get\Nto eat hot spring manju!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. These things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like that resilient part\Nof yours, Toyotomi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times I get Great\NMisfortune, I'll still draw a Lesser Luck at\Nthe end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Men these days have to\Nstick to it until the end!\NStickier than fermented beans!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stick to it so hard they'll\Nmake a fence out of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch over me Akina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Suuankou Tenpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I'll wait on it on the chun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Chun might be a hell wait, but as long as it's\Nnot in the dead wall, it's as good as mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As for 1p, as long as nobody has an\Nankou of it, it should still get dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I cut chun, then it'll be a 13p wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that... 3p would\Nmake it a simple sanankou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot possibly win this\Nhand as a mere sanankou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, to hell with it! There's no way they'll both\N get dropped in the same turn anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait on my 1p tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,3p!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Geh?! Don't drop a 1p on me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This one... Is unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To hell with your iipin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph... In the end, the true\Nessence of mahjong is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A breah holding race of four under a tub!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The first to come out of the water is the loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! The dream from this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one to raise his head loses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I cannot possibly afford to lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That got me by surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For me to get a Kokushi back-to-back... damn,\Nthis is some crazy luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at 47000.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,32000 here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 80000.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep a tab of it, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Akina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You left me all alone to play that mahjong\Nof yours again, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know someone like you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, there's a deeply profound reason behind all of thi-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A calm Autumn Day.\NWith it's vast clouds in the endless sky.\NCall for the eventual change of seasons.\NWhere through come summer and into spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:21:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lest will Toyotomi's spring ever arrive?\NI ask to the vast sky with it's red dragonflies.\NUnknowing to the path they thread\Nin the blue skies.\NTo which they reply, "Tomorrow shall come".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose, Toyotomi!"\N"Fight on, Toyotomi!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If we turn Toyotomi-kun into an augmented\Nsuperhuman mahjong machine,\Nhe might be capable of defeating the trio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And he might return to the old Toyotomi-kun if that happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time! Super Zugan
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Toyotomi Machine of Terror and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Some title but more importantly Akina butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it! Don't want to you to sleep on it!
